&lt;/div>&lt;h4 id="prev-pointing-at-right">&lt;code>prev&lt;/code> Pointing at Right&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>We know &lt;code>x&lt;/code> subtree is all printed, so all we need to do is to move &lt;code>x&lt;/code> upwards.&lt;/p>
